# ğŸ§© MGNREGA Performance Dashboard  

### ğŸ“Š Government Data Analytics & Visualization Platform  

The **MGNREGA Dashboard** is a full-stack web application that visualizes district-wise and state-level performance under the **Mahatma Gandhi National Rural Employment Guarantee Act (MGNREGA)**. It provides interactive charts, data insights, and statistics to monitor and analyze employment trends, expenditure, and performance metrics across India.  

