## ğŸš€ Features  

- âœ… **Interactive Visualization** â€“ Displays district-wise and state-level MGNREGA data using charts and graphs.  
- âœ… **Dynamic API Fetch** â€“ Fetches live performance data from MongoDB through backend APIs.  
- âœ… **Data Upload Support** â€“ Easily upload CSV files containing district performance metrics.  
- âœ… **Speech Integration** â€“ Text-to-speech functionality for accessibility and narration.  
- âœ… **Dockerized Setup** â€“ Fully containerized application for easy deployment.  
- âœ… **Responsive Frontend** â€“ Built with React and Tailwind CSS for seamless experience on all devices.  
- âœ… **RESTful Backend API** â€“ Node.js and Express backend serving data from MongoDB Compass.  

